OL,3,CAndy Burnham is 'extremely liberal',
OL,4,Csays Donald Trump in first verdict
OL,6,FAndy Burnham is "extremely liberal"
OL,7,Fand so "probably won't open up the
OL,8,FNorth Sea" for oil exploration, Donald
OL,9,FTrump has said.
OL,11,FIn his first public comments about the
OL,12,Fwould-be British prime minister, the
OL,13,FUS president described him as "the
OL,14,Fmayor of a town".
OL,16,FMr Trump also restated his
OL,17,Fdisappointment at the UK's response to
OL,18,Fthe Iran conflict, but believed Sir
OL,19,FKeir Starmer had "now gone".
OL,26,@nD@QOUnD@cO]oD@HOUpD@JO]uD@_OUvD@PO]{D@
OL,26,AROU{D@[O]
