OL,3,CAndy Burnham is 'extremely liberal',
OL,4,Csays Donald Trump in first verdict
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister will remain in post
OL,7,Funtil a successor is chosen, with Mr
OL,8,FBurnham, the newly elected MP and
OL,9,Fformer Greater Manchester mayor,
OL,10,Fcurrently the only contender for the
OL,11,Ftop job.
OL,13,FThe president had repeatedly lambasted
OL,14,FSir Keir over his energy stance and
OL,15,Fnot allowing further oil drilling in
OL,16,Fthe North Sea, relying instead on
OL,17,F"windmills".
OL,19,FMr Trump argued this had hurt the
OL,20,FPrime Minister "very, very badly".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@KO]|D@POU|D@aO]
