OL,3,CAndy Burnham is 'extremely liberal',
OL,4,Csays Donald Trump in first verdict
OL,6,FAsked at the White House what he knew
OL,7,Fabout Mr Burnham, the president said:
OL,8,F"I don't know, I think I see that he
OL,9,Fwas, I guess, the mayor of a town.
OL,11,F"I hear he's extremely liberal,
OL,12,Fextremely, so that means he probably
OL,13,Fwon't open up the North Sea.
OL,15,F"I gave Keir Starmer some pretty good
OL,16,Fadvice. I said open up the North Sea,
OL,17,Fgo to Aberdeen, which was the hottest
OL,18,Fcity of the whole continent.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782350285
OL,3,CAndy Burnham is 'extremely liberal',
OL,4,Csays Donald Trump in first verdict
OL,6,F"It was the oil city of Europe, and
OL,7,Fthey closed everything. It was
OL,8,Fterrible. I couldn't believe it.
OL,10,F"The North Sea is loaded. I have had
OL,11,Fevery oil company come to see me,
OL,12,F'Sir, could you give us access to the
OL,13,FUK? We would do anything to drill in
OL,14,Fthe North Sea'.
OL,16,F"The amazing thing is they buy their
OL,17,Foil from Norway, which gets the oil
OL,18,Ffrom the North Sea. Think of it, and
OL,19,Fthey pay a big premium.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
