CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782350285
OL,3,CAndy Burnham is 'extremely liberal',
OL,4,Csays Donald Trump in first verdict
OL,6,F"Norway's got now two trillion dollars
OL,7,Fin the bank, and the UK is dying, so
OL,8,Fthey should open up the North Sea, and
OL,9,Fit's an easy one, and a lot of good
OL,10,Fthings are going to happen. It's among
OL,11,Fthe greatest deals in the world."
OL,13,FMr Trump made his comments during a
OL,14,Fmeeting with Nato chief Mark Rutte
OL,15,Fahead of a crucial summit of the
OL,16,Fmilitary alliance in Turkey.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@aO]
