OL,3,CAndy Burnham is 'extremely liberal',
OL,4,Csays Donald Trump in first verdict
OL,6,FThe president has been scathing of
OL,7,Fallies, including the UK, for their
OL,8,Frefusal to be drawn into the war with
OL,9,FIran or help reopen the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz waterway after the US-Israeli
OL,11,Foffensive against Tehran effectively
OL,12,Fshut the key oil supply route.
OL,14,FSir Keir initially denied the US use
OL,15,Fof British military bases to conduct
OL,16,Fthe bombing campaign against Iran,
OL,17,Falthough limited permission was
OL,18,Fsubsequently granted for defensive
OL,19,Fstrikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
