OL,3,CAndy Burnham is 'extremely liberal',
OL,4,Csays Donald Trump in first verdict
OL,6,FThe conflict served to fuel existing
OL,7,Ftensions over Nato, with Mr Trump
OL,8,Farguing America had been bankrolling
OL,9,Fthe defence of other countries.
OL,11,FA row over UK military spending led
OL,12,FJohn Healey to recently quit as
OL,13,Fdefence secretary.
OL,15,FPraising Mr Rutte, Mr Trump said: "I
OL,16,Fthink if anybody else were in that
OL,17,Fposition, we wouldn't even be meeting
OL,18,Ftoday, to be honest with you, because
OL,19,Fwe were let down.
OL,26,@wD@cOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
