PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782350285
OL,3,CAndy Burnham is 'extremely liberal',
OL,4,Csays Donald Trump in first verdict
OL,6,F"We didn't need help on this at all.
OL,7,FWe demolished them (Iran) in literally
OL,8,Fthe first week, but it would have been
OL,9,Fnice if they would have said 'We'd
OL,10,Flike to help'.
OL,12,F"We didn't even need it, but it would
OL,13,Fhave been nice if they'd said, they
OL,14,Fdidn't say.
OL,16,F"I think if I would have called him
OL,17,F(Mr Rutte), he probably would have
OL,18,Ffound a way to help if we needed it. I
OL,19,Ffeel, you know, would have been a
OL,20,Flittle bit different."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU|D@VO]
