OL,3,CAndy Burnham is 'extremely liberal',
OL,4,Csays Donald Trump in first verdict
OL,6,FThe president added: "But I was
OL,7,Fdisappointed. I was disappointed with
OL,8,FItaly, I was disappointed with the UK.
OL,10,F"He (Sir Keir) has now gone, and you
OL,11,Fknow, he had a lot of problems, but we
OL,12,Fwere disappointed with the UK, we were
OL,13,Fdisappointed with Germany and France.
OL,14,FWe were disappointed with most of them.
OL,16,F"Spain is a horror show. Spain is
OL,17,Fterrible... I mean, they don't want to
OL,18,Fpay anything. They think they're in
OL,19,Ffor a free ride."
OL,26,@nD@VOUrD@AOUxD@AOU{D@QO]
