OL,3,CAndy Burnham is 'extremely liberal',
OL,4,Csays Donald Trump in first verdict
OL,6,FEarlier, Mr Rutte had sought to ease
OL,7,Ftensions with Mr Trump over Iran and
OL,8,Fthreats by the US to reduce troop
OL,9,Fnumbers in Europe.
OL,11,FThe Nato secretary general used bar
OL,12,Fchart displays, favoured by the
OL,13,Fpresident, to highlight the increased
OL,14,Fspending by Nato members, and hailed
OL,15,FMr Trump for bringing it about.
OL,17,FMr Rutte said: "I know there have been
OL,18,Fisolated cases about which you are
OL,19,Freally disappointed, but generally
OL,20,Fspeaking your European allies have
OL,21,Fbeen there with you."
OL,26,@yD@POU}D@UO]
