OL,3,CAndy Burnham is 'extremely liberal',
OL,4,Csays Donald Trump in first verdict
OL,6,FHe pointed out that up to to 5,000 US
OL,7,Fplanes took off from bases in Europe
OL,8,Fbefore Tehran and Washington agreed to
OL,9,Fa ceasefire.
OL,11,FMr Rutte added: "It would have been
OL,12,Fvery difficult to do Iran without
OL,13,Fhaving Europe as a power projection
OL,14,Fplatform for the United States."
